---
title     : GitHub Kaigi
bodyclass : index
layout    : layout
---

#main
  .text
    %section#section-detail.cols
      %h1 Details

      .col4
        %h2 What?
        %p
          GitHub KaigiはGitHub User Group主催のイベントであり、GitHubの正式なイベントではありません。
        %p
          GitHub Kaigi is an event organized by the GitHub User Group and is not an official GitHub event.

      .col4
        %h2 Where
        %p
          %a{href: "#", target: "_blank"} CyberAgent, Inc.
          %br
          SHIBUYA MARK CITY WEST
        %p
          %a{href: "#", target: "_blank"} Google Map

      .col4
        %h2 When?
        %p
          Sunday, June 1st 2014,
          1:00pm until 7:00pm

      .col4
        %h2 How?
        %p
          Doorkeeperから参加登録ができます
        %a{href: "", class: "btn-green"}
          Registration

    %section#section-time-table.cols
      %h1 Time table

      .col
        %ul.time-table-list
          - 10.times.each do
            %li
              .head
                .time
                  1:00 to 1:30
                .speaker-name
                  test
              .body
                Sign in and warm up

    %section#section-speaker.cols
      %h1 Spearker

      %ul.speaker-list
        - 4.times.each do
          %li.speaker-list-item
            .avatar
              %a{href: "#", target: "_blank"}
                %img{src: "", alt: ""}
            .names
              .fullname
                Full Name
              .username
                User Name
            .detail
              %i.icon-user
              Work Place

    %section#section-lt.cols
      %h1 LT

      .lt-guideline
        %p
          LT募集要項
      .nav-to-lt-form
        下記よりLTの応募をしてください。
        %a{href: "", class: "btn-green"}
          LT応募フォーム

    %section#section-team.cols
      %h1 Team

      %ul.team-list
        - data.team.each do |member|
          %li.team-list-item<>
            %a{href: "https://github.com/#{member.id}", target: "_blank"}
              %img{ src: "https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u//#{member.gravatar}?s=100", alt: 'Avatar' }
              %span.userid
                @#{member.id}

